cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing of instructional texts. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper discusses the development of machine learning approaches for parsing the text. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the paper deals with the conversion of protocols into a machine-readable format. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as the research aims to benefit biological research.
